reviewText: Love Tom Jones sexy as always. Thanks Castilla

This is a wonderful DVD of Tom (and guests), his voice never disappoints!  I was thrilled to be able to add this to my collection.  The picture and sound quality are great.  I will enjoy listening and watching this over & over.  As always, great picture of this beautiful man.
